fields.name: zookeeper-servers.xml
fields.text:
<zookeeper-servers>
{% for item in hosts['zookeeper'][zk_env][zk_group] %}
    <node index="{{ loop.index }}">
        <host>{{ item.host }}</host>
        <port>{{ item.port }}</port>
    </node>
{% endfor %}
</zookeeper-servers>

fields.name: storage.xml
fields.text:
<storage>
    <port>{{ storage_port }}</port>
    <hosts>
        {% for host in hosts.groups[storage_group] %}
        <host>{{ host.fqdn }}</host>
        {% endfor %}
    </hosts>
</storage>
